  {h : ‚ąÉ x ‚ąą support (Verifier.run_simulate őĻ oSpec StmtIn StmtOut n pSpec ŌÉ init impl verifier stmtIn tr), (x, witOut) ‚ąą relOut}
  (this : ¬¨if n = 0 then
      (stmtIn,
          @Extractor.RoundByRound.extractOut őĻ oSpec StmtIn WitIn WitOut n pSpec (fun x => WitIn)
