          relOut.language verifier stF (Fin.last n) stmtIn tr ‚ąß
        ‚ąÉ x ‚ąą support (Verifier.run_simulate őĻ oSpec StmtIn StmtOut n pSpec ŌÉ init impl verifier stmtIn tr),
