  The extractor processes rounds in decreasing order: `n ‚Üí n-1 ‚Üí ... ‚Üí 1 ‚Üí 0`, using
  intermediate witness types `WitMid m` for each round `m`.
-/
structure RoundByRound
    (oSpec : OracleSpec őĻ) (StmtIn WitIn WitOut : Type) {n : ‚Ąē} (pSpec : ProtocolSpec n)
    (WitMid : Fin (n + 1) ‚Üí Type) where
